### 1.3.3 LICENSE

Purpose: Define how others can use, modify, and distribute your code.

- Pick a license that matches your goals (e.g., MIT for maximum permissiveness).  
- Replace placeholders (`<YEAR>`, `<AUTHOR>`) before committing.

MIT License example:

```text
MIT License

Copyright (c) 2025 Stevan

Permission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining a copy...
[full text here]
